        <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/ATM#Flight"/>
        <rdfs:range rdf:resource="https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/NAS#NASday"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Links a flight with the day on which the flight arrives. This is the day determined by surveillance data sources to be the &apos;actual&apos; day of arrival, versus the scheduled day or the day specified in the flight plan, etc.</rdfs:comment>
